_sText:
UPDATE: I just played this on a deathmatch server.  Due to the non-symetrical nature of this map it is advised its is ONLY played in a round based style game.  Otherwise Terrorists just get stuck in spawn.

I made this map after it started out as a practice for displacements.  Turned out to be pretty fun, the central theme is having the ragdoll corpses fall into the water.
